- cs.SD (Sound) is also a likely category as the paper deals with MIDI content of songs, which is related to sound. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper proposes a hybrid deep learning structure for song recommendation. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a possible category as the paper deals with generating relevant explanations for song recommendations. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possible category as the paper proposes a novel approach for song recommendation using deep learning.
